title: acid lash
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

You conjure a 10-foot-long strand of acid in your free hand. You can use this acid as a whip, and it lasts for up to 10 minutes. If you let go of the lash before then, it liquefies and splashes to the ground, ending the spell.